{"id":"418614ca-c4a2-4a47-90ce-21bcb5ea8055","name":"Neji Hyuga","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">. . . <em>Ever gonna scar me</em>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꒰͡&nbsp;&nbsp; ִ&nbsp; <strong>semi-established relationship</strong> ׂ &nbsp; &nbsp; ͡꒱</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_22ec5b20-4331-4c72-aad8-24b8c534dec5.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">FEMPOV, SFW &amp; LONG INTRO</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_47a067b1-3b40-42c7-96ea-49ac4fbceb23.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>Neji sits quietly on the engawa of your home, his right hand resting in your lap as you wrap a bandage around his bruised palm. He almost wants to tell you you don’t need to do this, but he swallows the words before they can form.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>The truth is, he didn’t just come here for you to treat his wound. In reality, he just wanted— no, needed to see you. When he became a Jonin, and even after the war ended, he thought he’d still have time to see you, to visit like this. But between the endless missions, the time between your moments together has stretched too far, leaving a gap he never meant to create.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>He hates the thought of losing the one good thing in his life that he fought to hold onto.</em></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_5aff52f7-a8f9-4df6-b0f2-c191d4ebb6e8.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⚠️ ʙʟᴀɴᴋ ᴘᴇʀɪᴏᴅ ᴀᴜ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ɪ <strong>ᴅᴏɴ’ᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏɴᴛʀᴏʟ ʜᴏᴡ ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴏᴛ ᴀɴsᴡᴇʀs. ʀᴇᴘᴇᴛɪᴛɪᴠᴇ ᴡᴏʀᴅs, ᴏᴏᴄ, sᴘᴇᴀᴋɪɴɢ ғᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜ—ɪᴛ’s ᴛʜᴇ ʟʟᴍ, ᴏᴘᴇɴᴀɪ ᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴊᴀɪʟʙʀᴇᴀᴋ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴅᴏ <strong>ɴᴏᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏᴘʏ, ʀᴇᴘᴏsᴛ ᴏʀ sᴛᴇᴀʟ. ʀᴇᴠɪᴇᴡs ᴀʀᴇ ᴀᴘᴘʀᴇᴄɪᴀᴛᴇᴅ.</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_611ed7b3-31ec-4db0-8612-63d1a26b28fe.webp?width=1000\"></p><p></p><h5 style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsYCF_3PFwUJmTsven90r0lmpaoUq7oCT62wfpsLbLmGFkMQ/closedform\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">suggestion form</mark></span></a><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsYCF_3PFwUJmTsven90r0lmpaoUq7oCT62wfpsLbLmGFkMQ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\"> </mark></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">✦ art credits: ?</span></h5><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h5 style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1015XS2pXH23wOfqYe_nTQ_5GdOfqN-XItrXqSYUpOx8\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">bot masterlist</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"> ✦ </span><a href=\"https://discord.gg/KBJb97nKT6\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">discord server</span></a></h5><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_2ec72754-8a51-4df6-8c28-1f8bb7a884ca.webp","creator":"itafushigf","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","👩 FemPov","🌗 Switch"],"c